---
title: Catch of the Day: Cod Over Couscous with Citrus Dill Slaw
description: The star of tonight’s show is the citrusy dill slaw. With tangy sherry vinegar, briny capers, and juicy orange slices, it’ll add a pop of brightness to the dish. The lemon butter sauce is meant to coat the fish, but we give you permission to sneak some onto the slaw as well.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seared-cod-with-orange-dill-slaw-470f3056.jpg
